  <summary>Control your Elgato Stream Deck devices</summary>
	<description>
	  <p>Boatswain allows you to control Elgato Stream Deck devices.</p>
	  <p>With Boatswain you will be able to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Organize your actions in pages and profiles</li>
      <li>Set custom icons to actions</li>
      <li>Play sound effects during your streams</li>
      <li>Control OBS Studio using Stream Deck (requires the obs-websocket extension)</li>
    </ul>
	</description>

